    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Government response
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Response to media coverage of the UK government’s procurement of the Moderna vaccine
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The government, through the work of the Vaccine Taskforce, has put the UK in an extremely strong position if and when a vaccine meets robust standards of safety and effectiveness</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 17 November 2020
</div>

      <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata__other">
